OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776773466
OL,3,CMan opens fire on tourists at historic
OL,4,Cpyramids in Mexico, killing one
OL,6,FA man opened fire on tourists in
OL,7,FMexico on Monday, killing one Canadian
OL,8,Fand leaving at least 13 people injured.
OL,10,FThe shooting happened at the historic
OL,11,FTeotihuacan pyramids, an
OL,12,Farchaeological site north of Mexico's
OL,13,Fcapital, authorities said.
OL,15,FThose taken to hospitals for treatment
OL,16,Fwere six Americans, three Colombians,
OL,17,Fone Russian, two Brazilians and one
OL,18,FCanadian, the local government said.
OL,19,FThe youngest person who was injured
OL,20,Fwas 6; the oldest was 61, Mexican
OL,21,Fauthorities said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
