OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776773466
OL,3,CMan opens fire on tourists at historic
OL,4,Cpyramids in Mexico, killing one
OL,6,FMexico is one of three host countries
OL,7,Ffor the 2026 World Cup, alongside
OL,8,FCanada and the United States. Mexico
OL,9,FCity is one of the country's three
OL,10,Fhost cities, along with Guadalajara
OL,11,Fand Monterrey.
OL,13,FThe gunman was identified as 27-year-
OL,14,Fold Julio Cesar Jasso of Mexico, a
OL,15,Fstate official told the AP on
OL,16,Fcondition of anonymity because he is
OL,17,Fnot authorized to speak about the case.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
