FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776773466
OL,3,CMan opens fire on tourists at historic
OL,4,Cpyramids in Mexico, killing one
OL,6,FJasso later died from a self-inflicted
OL,7,Fgunshot wound, authorities said, and
OL,8,Fsecurity officials found a gun, a
OL,9,Fknife and ammunition. Jasso was the
OL,10,Fsole assailant in the attack, the
OL,11,FState of Mexico government confirmed
OL,12,Fon Monday night.
OL,14,FThe local government said seven people
OL,15,Fwere wounded by gunshots. How the
OL,16,Fother people were injured was not
OL,17,Fdisclosed, but a number of people fell
OL,18,Fwhen shooting started, some while
OL,19,Fclimbing on the pyramids.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
