OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776773466
OL,3,CMan opens fire on tourists at historic
OL,4,Cpyramids in Mexico, killing one
OL,6,FVideo and photos published by local
OL,7,Fmedia showed a man, later identified
OL,8,Fas Jasso, standing with a gun on top
OL,9,Fof a pyramid while people ducked for
OL,10,Fcover. A number of gunshots rang out
OL,11,Fin the videos.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
