PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776773466
OL,3,CMan opens fire on tourists at historic
OL,4,Cpyramids in Mexico, killing one
OL,6,FThe Teotihuacan pyramids, a UNESCO
OL,7,FWorld Heritage Site, are a series of
OL,8,Fmassive structures on the outskirts of
OL,9,FMexico City built by three different
OL,10,Fancient civilizations. As one of
OL,11,FMexico's most important touristic
OL,12,Fdestinations, the site drew more than
OL,13,F1.8 million international visitors
OL,14,Flast year, according to government
OL,15,Ffigures.
OL,17,FThe shooting took place shortly after
OL,18,F11:30 a.m. local time, when dozens of
OL,19,Ftourists were at the top of the
OL,20,FPyramid of the Moon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
