PN,31006
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776773466
OL,3,CMan opens fire on tourists at historic
OL,4,Cpyramids in Mexico, killing one
OL,6,F"Some people, because they were scared
OL,7,F... threw themselves face down on the
OL,8,Fground, and the rest of us started to
OL,9,Fgo down," a local guide said,
OL,10,Frecounting how the shooter, upon
OL,11,Fseeing the tourists descending the
OL,12,Fpyramid's steps, began firing.
OL,14,FAnother group of visitors lay
OL,15,Fmotionless on the pyramid's platform
OL,16,Fto avoid being targeted by the
OL,17,Fshooter, who authorities have not yet
OL,18,Fidentified.
