OL,3,CMan opens fire on tourists at historic
OL,4,Cpyramids in Mexico, killing one
OL,6,FBrenda Lee, of Vancouver, British
OL,7,FColumbia, said she was waiting to buy
OL,8,Fa souvenir when she and others in her
OL,9,Fgroup thought they heard firecrackers.
OL,11,F"Before we knew it, someone said, 'No,
OL,12,Fthat's gunfire, run,' and we saw
OL,13,Fpeople coming off the top," she told
OL,14,FCTV News, one of Canada's national
OL,15,Ftelevision broadcasters.
OL,17,F"There were thousands of people there
OL,18,Fand there were a lot of gunshots that
OL,19,Fjust kept coming," Lee said.
OL,26,@uD@[O]yD@AOU{D@RO]
