OL,3,CMan opens fire on tourists at historic
OL,4,Cpyramids in Mexico, killing one
OL,6,FThe scene quickly turned chaotic as
OL,7,Fpeople tried to escape.
OL,9,F"And then a fellow jumped," she said.
OL,10,F"It was someone trying to get away,
OL,11,Fand he dropped to the next level, but
OL,12,Fhe fell on his back, and it was ... it
OL,13,Fjust was awful."
