OL,3,CMan opens fire on tourists at historic
OL,4,Cpyramids in Mexico, killing one
OL,6,FIn past years, staff at the
OL,7,Farchaeological site carried out
OL,8,Fsecurity scans before people entered
OL,9,Fthe area but have since stopped, one
OL,10,Flocal guide noted.
OL,12,FMexican President Claudia Sheinbaum
OL,13,Fwrote on social media that the
OL,14,Fshooting would be investigated and
OL,15,Fthat she was in touch with the
OL,16,FCanadian Embassy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
