PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776773466
OL,3,CMan opens fire on tourists at historic
OL,4,Cpyramids in Mexico, killing one
OL,6,F"What happened today in Teotihuacan
OL,7,Fdeeply pains us. I express my most
OL,8,Fsincere solidarity with the affected
OL,9,Findividuals and their families," she
OL,10,Fwrote.
OL,12,FAnita Anand, Canada's foreign affairs
OL,13,Fminister, said on X that as a "result
OL,14,Fof a horrific act of gun violence, a
OL,15,FCanadian was killed and another
OL,16,Fwounded in Teotihuacan" and that her
OL,17,F"thoughts are with their family and
OL,18,Floved ones."
